<section>
  <h2>What We're Looking For</h2>
  <p>We accept guest blog submissions on a variety of topics, including (but not limited to):</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Digital marketing and advertising</li>
    <li>Content creation and SEO</li>
    <li>Small business and entrepreneurship</li>
    <li>Technology and innovation</li>
    <li>Lifestyle and personal development</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Your post should be between 800-1200 words and provide genuine value to our readers. We're looking for well-researched, informative, and unique content that aligns with our brand and audience.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>How to Submit</h2>
  <p>To submit a guest blog request, please fill out the form below with the following information:</p>
  <div class="guest-blog-form">
    <form>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="name">Name:</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="email">Email:</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="title">Blog Post Title:</label>
        <input type="text" id="title" name="title" required>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="summary">Summary:</label>
        <textarea id="summary" name="summary" rows="3" required></textarea>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="links">Previous Published Articles (optional):</label>
        <input type="text" id="links" name="links">
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit Request</button>
    </form>
  </div>
  <p>Once we review your request, we'll be in touch about next steps. Please note that we receive a high volume of submissions, so it may take us a few weeks to get back to you.</p>
</section>

